Wait in the car, please.

740
00:43:25,780 --> 00:43:28,577
Hold on.
I know who that is.

741
00:43:34,899 --> 00:43:36,414
Hello, Peter.

742
00:43:41,459 --> 00:43:43,416
I am starving.
I forgot to eat.

743
00:43:44,018 --> 00:43:45,419
Would you like something,
Peter?

744
00:43:45,579 --> 00:43:46,934
No, thanks.

745
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:48,215
You should eat.

746
00:43:48,300 --> 00:43:49,335
Don't fight.
She'll win.

747
00:43:49,459 --> 00:43:50,495
I will.

748
00:43:51,419 --> 00:43:52,739
Okay, yes.

749
00:43:53,539 --> 00:43:54,734
You want
some coffee?

750
00:43:54,939 --> 00:43:56,168
Yes, thanks.

751
00:43:56,659 --> 00:43:58,651
Do you have
any children?

752
00:44:00,179 --> 00:44:02,251
Two. A son and a daughter.

753
00:44:04,619 --> 00:44:05,609
Married?

754
00:44:06,419 --> 00:44:07,739
Divorced.

755
00:44:09,419 --> 00:44:11,092
What are their names,
your kids?

756
00:44:11,459 --> 00:44:15,419
There's Sarah. She's 11,
and Kevin is eight.

757
00:44:16,939 --> 00:44:17,929
Do you have any pictures?

758
00:44:23,459 --> 00:44:25,768
Fuck!
I lost my phone...

759
00:44:26,619 --> 00:44:28,850
Sorry, I should...
I gotta go...

760
00:44:28,939 --> 00:44:29,929
Peter, sit down.

761
00:44:30,059 --> 00:44:31,254
You're gonna
enjoy your sandwich,

762
00:44:31,339 --> 00:44:33,012
have some coffee
and stay the night.

763
00:44:37,099 --> 00:44:38,374
Milk and sugar?

764
00:44:40,260 --> 00:44:41,409
Black.

765
00:44:42,818 --> 00:44:43,809
Some fresh towels.

766
00:44:44,499 --> 00:44:46,252
There should be
soap and toothpaste,

767
00:44:46,379 --> 00:44:48,132
everything you
need in the bathroom.

768
00:44:48,339 --> 00:44:50,251
Thank you so
much for doing this.

769
00:44:50,339 --> 00:44:51,978
It's nothing.
Sleep well.

770
00:45:01,419 --> 00:45:02,455
What's going on, Peter?

771
00:45:07,179 --> 00:45:08,613
Talk to me.

772
00:45:12,619 --> 00:45:15,010
You think fresh towels
changes anything?

773
00:45:20,260 --> 00:45:21,249
Changes what?

774
00:45:21,339 --> 00:45:22,329
The shipyard.

775
00:45:25,339 --> 00:45:29,175
If I was home and you pulled that
shit, I'd beat the fuck out of you.

776
00:45:30,419 --> 00:45:33,617
I would crack your skull
on the pavement.

777
00:45:34,099 --> 00:45:35,533
That's why I came
over here today.

778
00:45:35,619 --> 00:45:38,293
To fuck you up for
what you made me do.

779
00:45:39,379 --> 00:45:40,608
I don't care how nice
you're being to me.

780
00:45:40,699 --> 00:45:41,689
I don't give a shit.

781
00:45:42,179 --> 00:45:44,010
I'm gonna
wake up tomorrow,

782
00:45:45,859 --> 00:45:47,213
and all these people,

783
00:45:53,219 --> 00:45:54,699
all my friends,

784
00:45:56,899 --> 00:45:58,094
are still fucked.

785
00:45:59,899 --> 00:46:01,253
And I'm still fucked.

786
00:46:04,619 --> 00:46:06,611
You fucked all of us.

787
00:46:07,979 --> 00:46:10,289
But I'm gonna
get blamed for it.

788
00:46:11,619 --> 00:46:14,373
So, now I have to carry that
weight on my shoulders.

789
00:46:23,419 --> 00:46:25,217
You fucked me, Frank.

790
00:46:27,099 --> 00:46:29,251
I shouldn't have let you
do it, but I did...

791
00:46:48,539 --> 00:46:50,178
Are you done now?

792
00:46:53,419 --> 00:46:55,092
Get up.

793
00:46:59,139 --> 00:47:00,129
No.

794
00:47:00,219 --> 00:47:02,893
I said get up.
And follow me.

795
00:47:03,739 --> 00:47:04,809
Now.

796
00:47:20,939 --> 00:47:21,929
Get in.

797
00:47:23,300 --> 00:47:25,609
Take off your clothes
and get in.

798
00:47:25,699 --> 00:47:26,689
Do it. Now.

799
00:47:47,419 --> 00:47:51,050
There was a DNC meeting earlier this week.
About the Governor's race.

800
00:47:51,499 --> 00:47:53,695
Your name came up as someone
we might want to run.

801
00:47:56,179 --> 00:47:58,056
Aspirin. Go ahead.

802
00:48:02,018 --> 00:48:04,409
Everyone in that room wanted
to cross you off the list.

803
00:48:04,499 --> 00:48:06,172
I said no.
I stuck up for you.

804
00:48:06,499 --> 00:48:08,172
I said, "Peter Russo,
he's got potential.

805
00:48:09,539 --> 00:48:12,054
"He's young, he's capable,
he's going places."

806
00:48:14,018 --> 00:48:16,329
I made them keep you
in contention.

807
00:48:16,579 --> 00:48:18,617
You're still
on that list.

808
00:48:20,059 --> 00:48:24,531
You show up at my house in the middle
of the night, drunk, to whine?

809
00:48:25,379 --> 00:48:27,371
To try to shift
the blame on me?

810
00:48:27,459 --> 00:48:30,850
Instead of taking responsibility
for yourself and your own actions?

811
00:48:32,818 --> 00:48:34,014
Maybe they were right
in that meeting.

812
00:48:36,659 --> 00:48:38,059
Maybe you are worthless.

813
00:48:41,018 --> 00:48:43,614
I'm the only person who
believes in you, Peter,

814
00:48:43,699 --> 00:48:46,168
but maybe
that's one too many.

815
00:48:48,699 --> 00:48:50,896
The hot water will
open up your capillaries.

816
00:48:51,179 --> 00:48:53,693
The aspirin you just took
will make your blood thinner.

817
00:48:53,780 --> 00:48:55,691
It's up to you, Peter...

818
00:48:57,619 --> 00:48:59,975
And if you do decide to
take the coward's way out,

819
00:49:00,139 --> 00:49:03,893
cut along the tracks, not across them.
That's a rookie mistake.

820
00:49:24,659 --> 00:49:26,332
Morning.
Morning.

821
00:49:28,260 --> 00:49:29,579
You need a lift
to the Hill?

822
00:49:29,659 --> 00:49:31,172
I should go home
and change my clothes.

823
00:49:31,260 --> 00:49:32,931
No, no,
we'll drop you.

824
00:49:33,818 --> 00:49:35,572
You want some coffee?

825
00:49:47,739 --> 00:49:48,729
Frank?

826
00:49:48,818 --> 00:49:49,809
One month.

827
00:49:51,499 --> 00:49:52,489
Hmm?

828
00:49:52,619 --> 00:49:54,452
One month sober.

829
00:50:00,539 --> 00:50:01,768
I can give you that.

830
00:50:03,179 --> 00:50:04,977
Not for me. For you.

831
00:50:10,300 --> 00:50:12,335
Has the seed
been planted?

832
00:50:12,659 --> 00:50:15,175
Only Peter can
answer that question.

833
00:50:15,459 --> 00:50:16,813
He has a choice.

834
00:50:17,459 --> 00:50:18,734
Will he wither?

835
00:50:18,818 --> 00:50:20,731
Or will he thrive?

836
00:50:21,219 --> 00:50:22,652
Only time will tell.

